&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Donorbox&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Donorbox is a leading fundraising platform and donor management system for nonprofit organizations. Our mission is to accelerate positive impact worldwide by helping nonprofits become highly effective at raising funds and managing their supporter base. Since 2014, we have powered more than 100,000 global organizations to close to $3B in donations. 🚀&lt;/p&gt;
