&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Serve as the primary operational partner to the SVP of Growth &amp;amp; Global Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare meeting briefs, agendas, summaries, action items, and follow-ups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Track the SVP&#39;s priorities, commitments, and key initiatives to ensure nothing falls through the cracks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Attend key meetings, capture decisions and action items, and drive follow-through across teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organize information and surface risks, blockers, and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help ensure strategic decisions are executed effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track company initiatives, timelines, owners, and deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
