&lt;p&gt;Donorbox is seeking a Product Analyst to join our growing team. Reporting directly to the Group Product Manager, the person will be a key player in helping our product teams make data-driven decisions. The role’s primary focus will be on defining, implementing, and analyzing product metrics such as in-app events and conversion funnels. The person will also be responsible for ensuring the integrity and accuracy of our data collection, acting as a crucial link between our Product and Data departments. They will work closely with product managers and designers to provide the insights they need to build and iterate on successful features, and track the key results for each objective of every product team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
