&lt;li&gt;Secure the user journey by shipping product changes to our user onboarding to better capture verification data while maintaining a seamless activation flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship internal tooling to empower our support teams to quickly identify and take action on bad actors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure monitors and alarms through vendors like Stripe Radar to proactively mitigate risk and decrease scammers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and mitigate link spam that degrades Donorbox&#39;s domain authority and search ranking, including in AI-powered search tools and answer engines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommend and collaborate with other Service and Product Line engineering teams on changes within their remit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Site Reliability Engineering (SRE) to improve WAF rules and platform monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Payments team on refund and chargeback workflows to mitigate financial risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage platform integrity by overseeing policies around User Generated Content, Content Safety, Spam, and Terms of Service (TOS) violations.&lt;/li&gt;
