&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;The CRM was launched in early 2026 on the back of a beta that drew thousands of leads. Today, it does the core jobs well and is ready for thoughtful stewardship into a market-leading product.&lt;/p&gt;
