&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sharpen segmentation and Lists&lt;/strong&gt;: Enable nonprofits with powerful filtering and the path toward data-informed segmentation that nonprofits need.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grow CRM as an acquisition engine:&lt;/strong&gt; Ship top-of-funnel features that pull new organizations into the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make communications demonstrably drive giving&lt;/strong&gt;: Own the insights and metrics that help nonprofits use email and direct stewardship to uplift their fundraising.&lt;/li&gt;
